Package ScheduleModel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ScheduleModel  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Class
    This class describes a Class (a group of students) with the properties of its:
         • Name (unique Name, can't be the same for multiple classes)
         • attending students
    Date
    This class describes date and time, down to minute precision.
    Exam
    This class describes an Exam, with the properties of its:
         • Name
         • Place (where the exam takes place)
         • Participating Class
         • Examiner
         • Requirements (for the classroom)
         • Start Date
         • Duration (in minutes)
    Examiner
    This class describes a person (an Examiner) with the properties of his or her:
         • Name (unique Name, can't be the same for multiple examiners)
         • time intervals when he or she is unavailable
    ExamPeriod
    This class describes an ExamPeriod which defines this examination period by the following attributes:
         • ValidDates, a list of valid dates when exams can take place
         • StartTime, the time from when exams can take place on a valid date
         • EndTime, the time from when exams can not take place on a valid date
         • BreakStartTime, the time after the break takes place for the examiners of the oral exams and the project exams
         • BreakEndTime, the time before the break takes place for the examiners of the oral exams and the project exams
         • BreakDuration, the duration (in minutes) of the break for the examiners of the oral exams and the project exams
         • DefaultDurationPerStudent, default duration (in minutes) per student for OralExams
         • DefaultDurationPerStudentPerGroup, default duration (in minutes) per student, per group for ProjectExams
         • DefaultBreakDurationPerStudent, default break duration (in minutes) per student for OralExams
         • DefaultBreakDurationPerGroup, default break duration (in minutes) per group for ProjectExams
    OralExam
    This class describes an OralExam, by extending the Exam class with its specific methods and attributes, like:
         • a second Examiner
         • DurationPerStudent (in minutes)
         • BreakDurationPerStudent (in minutes)
    ProjectExam
    This class describes a ProjectExam, by extending the Exam class with its specific methods and attributes, like:
         • a second Examiner
         • DurationPerStudentPerGroup (in minutes)
         • BreakDurationPerGroup (in minutes)
    Room
    This class describes a classroom with the properties of its:
         • Name (unique Name, can't be the same for multiple rooms)
         • Size
         • Equipments
    ScheduleModelManager
    This class manages other a classes' instances which are needed to to create the exam schedule.
    Student
    This class describes a person (a Student) with the properties of his or her:
         • Name
         • VIAID (unique ID, can't be the same for multiple students)
         • the name of the Class that he or she attends
         • the project group which he or she is being part of
    WrittenExam
    This class describes a WrittenExam, by extending the Exam class with its specific methods.
